description: A Moroccan influenced spicy chicken dish.
keywords: Tagine,Tree nut free,Chicken,Sesame free,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Spicy Chicken Tagine Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 400g chickpeas, store bought tin and drained
400g chicken breasts, cooked and cut into chunks
2 large white onion, peeled and chopped
100g lentils, cooked as per packet instructions

recipeInstructions.text: Heat up an oven safe dish on the pan with the oil and fry the onions, garlic, carrot, parsnip and chicken for 6 minutes while mixing.
Add the rest of the ingredients to the oven safe dish apart from the couscous and combine well, cover and place in the oven.
Allow the dish to cook for 45 minutes.
Cook the couscous as per packet instructions and then drain.
Serve the drained couscous with the tagine ingredients from the oven.
